reviews.text:
If you love the general profile of this juice, You HAVE to mix it! The batch was steeping for 3 weeks and it was great. This time i will wait a little longer, to see what happen, if the taste change in a good way.! But its really nice after 3 weeks. All flavours blends together well.&#xD;
I get a little dry cake texture , but in a good way. Followed of a creamy, delish Strawberry frosting. The lemon from the pandorra is gone. The mix has the right amount of flavour, to be a Allday. Great work Thadentman!&#xD;
UPDATE: Also after 5 weeks the flavours hold. All flavours are blends together even better. Harmonie between the Strawberry, cake and frosting!
